import moment from 'moment' import '../css/SummaryCard.css' function SummaryCard({day}) { const day_icon = `${process.env.REACT_APP_ICON_URL + day.weather[0]["icon"]}@2x.png` return (

  • {Math.round(day.main.temp)}°C

    {day.weather[0].main}

    {day.weather[0].description}

    {moment(day.dt_txt).format("hh:mm a")}

    • ) } export default SummaryCard
